The Style Contest That’s Going Places! ✈️💃

She’s planning a getaway — and her outfit could win her a BIBA voucher! #BIBATravelDiaries is ON.

Jet-setting, road-tripping, or staycationing — wherever she’s headed, this is her moment to shine in BIBA.

How to Enter:
💬 Step 1: Comment on our contest post —
“What is BIBA about you?”

📸 Step 2 (Bonus but fab):
 • Post a pic of yourself or your little one in a BIBA outfit — from a trip, celebration, or memory
 • OR visit a BIBA UAE store, try on your fav outfit & snap a selfie
 📲 Tag @bibauae, use #BIBATravelDiaries, and tag 2 friends who’d love to join the fun!

🎁 Win:
• 3 Women – AED 350 vouchers
• 3 Girls – AED 250 vouchers
*T&Cs apply

This isn’t just a contest.
It’s her story. Her style. Her BIBA moment. 💫

📍 Visit us:
Dubai – BurJuman, Deira City Centre
Sharjah – City Centre Al Zahia
Abu Dhabi – Al Wahda Mall
